Chapter 6 - Types, Constants, and Global Functions / Types and Constants
Cyberdog Services

Proxy Scheme

The kCyberProxyScheme constant is a string constant ("cyberproxy:") that represents the URL scheme for a proxy server. A Cyberdog service that wants to provide proxy services must include this scheme in the list of URL schemes that it supports.
